data.description: Telfair Grove @ River Green Beauty with Master on Main. Open Floor Plan features 2-Story Foyer, Dining Room, Separate Living Room/Office, Large Family Room w/Dramatic Curved Wall of Windows and Chef's Kitchen w/Granite Counters, S/S Appliances, Double Ovens, Gas Cooktop & Built-In Microwave. Master Suite offers Trey Ceilings and Lux Bath. Upstairs offers a large Loft area with curved wall of windows, 3 spacious Bedrooms (one with a full en-suite bath and the other two with a Jack/Jill Bath). Many upgrades include Hardwoods on main, Coffered & Vaulted Ceilings, Arched Doorways, Stone Fireplace with Built-In Bookshelves & Iron Spindles.  Huge daylight Terrace Level is perfect for Entertaining w/semi-finished Game Room, Area stubbed for Bath and many large rooms ready for future living space or storage. The back deck is perfect for grilling and overlooks the fenced backyard. New Hi-Eff HVAC Units, New Interior Paint. Private lot with flat extended driveway that leads to the 3 car garage and is across the street from to Clubhouse & Pools, Walk to Tennis Courts, Basketball Court & Playground. This Home is a MUST-SEE!
